BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (helped each other.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (Amara had painted the village back to life. But more than that, her generosity had) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (inspired others.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (Farmers shared their harvests. Builders helped fix each other's homes. Children helped) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (younger children learn.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (Amara's brush had started something, and the village's own kindness kept it going.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: A thriving, beautiful village with happy people working together, gardens) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (blooming, children playing, a community transformed by generosity and mutual support]) Tj ET
