BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Amara also discovered something beautiful   the brush worked best when she was joyful) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (while painting.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (If she painted while feeling grateful and happy, the colors were brighter, the food) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (tastier, the blankets warmer.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (But if she painted out of duty or resentment, the results were ordinary.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td ('Paint with love,' the brush whispered to her. 'That's the real ingredient. Not magic  ) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (love.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (And Amara did. Every single day, with love.) Tj ET
