BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 24) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (Here are some ways YOUR gifts can be a magic paintbrush:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (If you are good at reading, read to someone who is learning. If you are good at sports,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (teach a younger child to play.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (If you are funny, make someone laugh on their worst day. If you are a good listener, sit) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (with someone who needs to talk.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (If you can draw, make art that makes people smile. If you are strong, carry something) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (heavy for someone who cannot.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (Every gift shared is a painting brought to life. Every talent used for others is magic) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 578.2 Td (made real.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td ([Illustration: Children using different gifts to help each other   reading together,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (teaching sports, making art for others   each child's hands glowing like they hold a magic) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 526.4 Td (brush]) Tj ET
endstream
