BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 25) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (And remember Amara's most important lesson:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (The joy of using your gift for yourself lasts a moment. The joy of using it for others) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (lasts forever.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (So paint your world with generosity. Use what you have been given to make life more) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (beautiful for everyone around you.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (That is the real magic. Not in the brush. In the heart that chooses to share.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (Your heart. Your gift. Your magic. Go paint something wonderful.) Tj ET
