BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (The Moral of the Story) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Use Your Gifts to Help Others, Not Just Yourself) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.4 Td (Amara discovered that her magic paintbrush grew stronger when she used it for others and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.4 Td (faded when she used it selfishly. Our gifts and talents work the same way! When we share) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.4 Td (what we're good at with others   helping, teaching, creating, comforting   it brings us) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.4 Td (more happiness than keeping everything for ourselves. Your unique ability is meant to make) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.4 Td (the world better. So share it freely, and watch it grow.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
