BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (After reading this story together, talk about these questions:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.4 Td (1. What gifts or talents do YOU have? \(Remember, a gift can be anything   kindness counts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.4 Td (too!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.6 Td (2. How could you use your gift to help someone else this week?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.8 Td (3. Why do you think the brush stopped working when Amara was selfish, and grew stronger) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.8 Td (when she was generous?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 557.0 Td (4. Have you ever felt really good after helping someone? What did you do?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 533.2 Td (5. If you had Amara's magic paintbrush for one day, what would you paint to help people?) Tj ET
